FRDM-TFC IO MAP
===============

PTA2:1	UART0 TX:RX
PTA2:1	Cadence sensors 1:0

PTB1:0	 Servo
PTB2	 Potentiometer 1 (ADC) 
PTB3	 Potentiometer 0 (ADC)
PTB11:8	 LEDs
PTB19:18 Cadence sensors 1:0

PTC4:1   H-bridge PWM
PTC9:8	 Cadence sensors 3:2
PTC11:10 (Option) Linescan 1 CLK/SI
PTC12    (Option) Linescan 1 CLK
PTC13	 Button 0
PTC16    (Option) Linescan 1 SI
PTC17	 Button 1

PTD0	 HC05 cmd
PTD5	 Linescan 0 (ADC)
PTD6	 Linescan 1 (ADC)
PTD7	 Linescan 0 SI

PTE0 	 HC05 power
PTE1 	 Linescan 0 CLK
PTE5:2 	 4-way switch
PTE20	 H-bridge fault
PTE21	 H-bridge enable
PTE21	 Battery voltage (ADC) - not muxed.
PTE22	 Motor 1 current (ADC)
PTE23	 Motor 0 current (ADC)
PTE25:24 Accelerometer (I2C) - fixed.
PTE30:29 (Option) Linescan 1 CLK/SI (Analogue out)
